Barclays Bank Leads Ring-Fence Deal, Sunday Telegraph Reports

-- B y   C a t h e r i n e   A i r l i e
-- 
2011-04-03T08:39:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-03/barclays-bank-leads-ring-fence-deal-sunday-telegraph-reports.html
Barclays Bank Plc is leading a
proposal for U.K. banks to  “ring-fence”  services to protect
taxpayers from another financial crisis, the Sunday Telegraph
reported, citing submissions to the  Independent Commission on
Banking .  The commission’s interim report on the banking industry,
due April 11, will say banks exaggerate the threat of new rules,
the newspaper said without citing where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
